<v t="swot.20260309094910.19"><vh>依赖范围说明</vh></v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.20"><vh>Maven 生命周期</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.21"><vh>Maven 内置插件介绍</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.22" descendentVnodeUnknownAttributes="7d71005803000000302e3271017d71025808000000616e6e6f7461746571037d71042858080000007072696f7269747971054d0f27580a000000707269736574646174657106580a000000323032352d30382d333071077573732e"><vh>Maven 高级 -- 学完 spring boot 再来</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.23"><vh>分模块设计</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.24"><vh>先预览一下创建好的 maven 模块结构</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.25"><vh>创建空的 maven 项目</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.26"><vh>复制之前的 general-manager 项目</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.27"><vh>创建 maven 模块 general-pojo</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.28"><vh>创建 maven 模块 general-utils</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.29"><vh>在模块 general-manager 的 pom.xml 中引入新建的两个模块</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.30"><vh>@ignore-node file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-manager/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.31"><vh>@ignore-node dependencies</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.32"><vh>@ignore-tree dependency</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.33"><vh>jjwt</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.34"><vh>fastjson2</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.35"><vh>aop</vh></v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.36"><vh>general-pojo</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.37"><vh>general-utils</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.38"><vh>测试分模块后的项目</vh></v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.39"><vh>继承关系</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.40"><vh>创建父模块（接着上面分模块设计继续操作）</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.41"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-parent/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.42"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.43"><vh>1) packaging 指定该父模块打包方式为 pom</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.44"><vh>2) parent 指定该模块的父模块依赖 Spring Boot 默认的 &lt;parent&gt;</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.45"><vh>3) dependency 配置各个子模块共有的依赖（子模块会自动继承父模块的依赖）</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.46"><vh>在子模块的 pom.xml 文件中，配置继承关系</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.47"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-manager/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.48"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.49"><vh>parent &amp; self</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.50"><vh>@ignore-tree dependencies</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.51"><vh>dependency</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.52"><vh>jjwt</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.53"><vh>fastjson2</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.54"><vh>aop</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.55"><vh>general-pojo</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.56"><vh>general-utils</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.57"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-pojo/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.58"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.59"><vh>parent &amp; self</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.60"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-utils/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.61"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.62"><vh>parent &amp; self</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.63" descendentVnodeUnknownAttributes="7d710058010000003071017d71025808000000616e6e6f7461746571037d71042858080000007072696f7269747971054d0f27580a000000707269736574646174657106580a000000323032352d30382d333071077573732e"><vh>父模块版本锁定</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.64"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-parent/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.65"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.66"><vh>@ignore-node 1) packaging 指定该父模块打包方式为 pom</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.67"><vh>@ignore-node 2) parent 指定该模块的父模块依赖 Spring Boot 默认的 &lt;parent&gt;</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.68"><vh>@ignore-node 3) dependency 配置各个子模块共有的依赖（子模块会自动继承父模块的依赖）</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.69"><vh>dependencyManagement -&gt; 在此父模块中指定依赖版本</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.70"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-utils/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.71"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.72"><vh>@ignore-node parent &amp; self</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.73"><vh>&lt;dependencies&gt;</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.74"><vh>父模块中引用依赖的自定义版本属性</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.75"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-parent/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.76"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.77"><vh>@ignore-node 1) packaging 指定该父模块打包方式为 pom</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.78"><vh>@ignore-node 2) parent 指定该模块的父模块依赖 Spring Boot 默认的 &lt;parent&gt;</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.79"><vh>properties -&gt; 在此自定义依赖版本变量来统一管理依赖版本号</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.80"><vh>dependency           -&gt; 在此引用自定义的依赖版本变量</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.81"><vh>dependencyManagement -&gt; 在此引用自定义的依赖版本变量</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.82"><vh>面试题: &lt;dependencyManagement&gt; 与 &lt;dependencies&gt;的区别是什么?</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.83"><vh>聚合模块</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.84"><vh>file -&gt; module-design/maven-general-manager/general-parent/pom.xml</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.85"><vh>@ignore-node &lt;project&gt;</vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.86"><vh>@ignore-tree </vh>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.87"><vh>1) packaging 指定该父模块打包方式为 pom</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.88"><vh>2) parent 指定该模块的父模块依赖 Spring Boot 默认的 &lt;parent&gt;</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.89"><vh>properties -&gt; 在此自定义依赖版本变量来统一管理依赖版本号</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.90"><vh>dependency -&gt; 在此引用自定义的依赖版本变量</vh></v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.91"><vh>dependencyManagement -&gt; 在此引用自定义的依赖版本变量</vh></v>
</v>
<v t="swot.20260309094910.92"><vh>modules -&gt; 配置聚合模块的子模块</vh></v>
</v>
</v>
</v>
